<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id62b7a13d-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa" identifier="/us/usc/t25/s3120"><num value="3120">§ 3120.</num><heading> Trust responsibility</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Nothing in this chapter shall be construed to diminish or expand the trust responsibility of the United States toward Indian forest lands, or any legal obligation or remedy resulting therefrom.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id62b7a13e-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/101/630/tIII/s321">Pub. L. 101–630, title III, § 321</ref>, <date date="1990-11-28">Nov. 28, 1990</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/104/4544">104 Stat. 4544</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
